headline: LKQ Corporation to Present at Upcoming Investor Conference
summary: ANTIOCH, Tenn., Oct. 27, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- LKQ Corporation (Nasdaq: LKQ), today announced that members of its senior management will be presenting at the following investor conference: Gabelli Funds 49th Annual Automotive SymposiumNovember 4, 2025Las Vegas, Nevada Materials used during the presentation will be posted to the Company's website: www.lkqcorp.com on the day of the conference.
